<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFEF6A50F7F690451695BD0F" authorityName="Kaup" authorityYear="1829" box="[2058,2197,1564,1597]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Pipistrellus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="778" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Pipistrellus</taxonomicName>
is uncertain, but it seems to be similar to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFEF6A50F76B901A1725BD56" baseAuthorityName="Temminck" baseAuthorityYear="1838" box="[2199,2341,1603,1636]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Pipistrellus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="778" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="abramus">P. abramus</taxonomicName>
